    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2003-04-02</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2003-08-27T21:33:13Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Credit Card Consumer Protection Act of 2003 - Amends Truth in Lending Act with respect to open-end consumer credit card plan disclosures to require: (1) a 30-day posting deadline for the mailing of credit card account statements; (2) prominent type face disclosure of the date by which a late fee will be charged to the account; and (3) recordkeeping by the credit card issuer of the pertinent dates for the mailing of bills and receipt of bill payments. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Credit Card Consumer Protection Act of 2003</title>
